<li><i>Tangled Up</i> (1985)<sup id="cite&#95;ref-150" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-150"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>149<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup></li>
<li><i>Mind Vampires</i> (1986)<sup id="cite&#95;ref-151" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-151"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>150<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Neighbourhood_Watch_(short_story)" title="Neighbourhood Watch (short story)">Neighbourhood Watch</a></i> (1987)</li>
<li><i>Scatter My Ashes</i> (1988)<sup id="cite&#95;ref-152" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-152"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>151<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup></li>
<li><i>The Extra</i> (1990)<sup id="cite&#95;ref-153" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-153"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>152<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup></li>
<li><i>The Vat</i> (1990)<sup id="cite&#95;ref-154" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-154"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>153<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup></li>
<li><i>In Numbers</i> (1991)</li>
<li><i>The Demon's Passage</i> (1991)<sup id="cite&#95;ref-155" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-155"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>154<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup></li>
<li><i>Fidelity</i> (1991)</li>
<li><i>Before</i> (1992)</li>
<li><i>Dust</i> (1992)<sup id="cite&#95;ref-156" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-156"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>note 2<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup></li>
<li><i>Worthless</i> (1992)<sup id="cite&#95;ref-157" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-157"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>155<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup></li>
<li><i>Reification Highway</i> (1992)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Wang%27s_Carpets" title="Wang&#39;s Carpets">Wang's Carpets</a></i> (1995)<sup id="cite&#95;ref-158" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-158"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>note 3<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup></li>
<li><i>Yeyuka</i> (1997)<sup id="cite&#95;ref-159" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-159"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>156<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Schild%27s_Ladder#Background" title="Schild&#39;s Ladder">Only Connect</a></i> (2000)<sup id="cite&#95;ref-160" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-160"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>157<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup></li>
<li><i>In the Ruins</i> (2013)<sup id="cite&#95;ref-161" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-161"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>158<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Didicosm" title="Didicosm">Didicosm</a></i> (2023)</li>
<li><i>Death and the Gorgon</i> (2024)</li>
<li><i>Vouch for Me</i> (2024)</li></ul></div>
